{"about_the_game":"TITANS have long been mere stories, but soon twin protagonists Torden and Jorden are going to experience the thunderous rise of the long-dormant creatures.<br><br>Inspired by Celtic mythology, TITANKIN Prologue takes you on a tight JRPG-style adventure where you'll meet plenty of colourful characters, wield the power of TITANS, and enjoy thoughtful turn-based battles in a delightfully crafted pixel-art world.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451760/extras/FeaturesOf.png?t=1629778190\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Strategic Turn-Based Combat</strong><br>Each enemy you encounter has distinct strengths and weaknesses - discover and employ your own strategies to quickly overthrow the enemy.  <br></li><li> <strong>Command TITANS</strong><br>Defeating each TITAN will yield a KINSTONE- equip one on a character and they\u2019ll benefit from enhanced stat growth, as well as the ability to call upon the TITAN in battle!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451760/extras/TITAN_POWRIE-FIN2.png?t=1629778190\" /> <br></li><li> <strong>The Classic JRPG, Modernized</strong><br>No random encounters: on-map enemies will chase or run from the player, and superior balancing removes the need to grind for levels. Save points within a dungeon will also fully restore the party!<br></li><li><strong>Vibrant Celtic-Mythology Setting</strong><br>You will meet, battle, and recruit creatures and entities inspired by famous and obscure mythical stories of Ireland, Scotland, Wales, and more.<br></li><li> <strong>Short and Sweet</strong><br>This opening act of the TITANKIN saga won't devour all your time- if you love JRPGs but don't have 50+ hours to spend on a juggernaut, TITANKIN Prologue will leave you feeling fulfilled.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451760/page_bg_generated_v6b.